OOC- I woke up this morning thinking it was going to be just a plain average 
day in the NBW...but Kslawdogg informed me he is on vacation and left me some 
of his characters. These charaters include several Maximals...and being the 
Predacon Commander you can bet I am thrilled.

~~~~~~~~~~

::: Chordate looked at the Maximals coming and going, moving in and out of 
the ship he was in command of at the moment. He liked being in control of the 
movement, and setting up the new base. ::

::: Chordate looked over to Smokescreen and Ramhorn ::: You two, front and 
center!

::: Ramhorn and Smokescreen shuffle there way forward. :::

::: Ramhorn ::: Yes?

::: Chordate :::Please tell me why your not monitoring the perimiter of the 
ship!

::: Smokescreen hesitates ::: We were never told to....sir.

::: Sir, he liked that. Chordate continued ::: We have three Predacons 
outside snapping pictures of this base like it were a swimsuit modle in thong!

::: Ramhorn and Smokescreen turned to see Doublepunch, Injector, and 
Manterror outside. :::

::: Chordate ::: Well? Arent you going to stop them?!!!!!

::: The Maximals looked at each other and ran to the main exit and began to 
blast the hidden Predacons. :::

~~~~~~~~~~

::: Hell Beast looked to Brightblade ::: Yes Subcommander, you may go on your 
mission if you wish. I think it would be wise.

~~~~~~~~~~

:::: Double Punch, Manterror, and Injector watch the two Maximals come 
forward and begin to blast blindly. :::

::: Double Punch ::: Fools! Kil them!

::: Injector laughs as he shoots another Cyberbee at the two Predacons and it 
explodes. ::::
